OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night to come, with
OL,7,Fsome light drizzle and hill fog across
OL,8,Fwestern hills. Some clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping towards the east allowing
OL,10,Fmist patches to form. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,13,Fsome mist and light rain over hills.
OL,14,FTurning brighter through the
OL,15,Fafternoon, especially further east.
OL,16,FFeeling warm, particularly in the
OL,17,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
