OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,7,Fwinds, though breezier across hills
OL,8,Fand on Friday. Temperatures
OL,9,Fincreasing, becoming very warm or hot.
OL,10,FPerhaps an isolated heavy shower on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
